+// Copyright (c) 2026 The DIG Network Authors. All rights reserved.
+// Use of this source code is governed by a BSD-style license that can be
+// found in the LICENSE file.
+//
+// Browser-process URLLoaderFactory for the native dig:// scheme (DIG Browser).
+//
+// Network-service top-level navigations and subresource loads do NOT consult
+// the //net URLRequestContext job factory, so the legacy net::URLRequestJob
+// path (net/url_request/dig_protocol_handler.*) never runs for a dig://
+// navigation. This factory plugs dig:// into the non-network URLLoaderFactory
+// machinery (CreateNonNetworkNavigationURLLoaderFactory /
+// RegisterNonNetworkSubresourceURLLoaderFactories in
+// chrome_content_browser_client.cc) so dig:// resolves natively, end-to-end.
+//
+// It follows the SAME contract as the reference dig-chrome-extension and the
+// ported net::dig::* crypto core (see SYSTEM.md "JSON-RPC 2.0 read methods"):
+//
+//   1. Parse the URN (net::dig::ParseDigUrn).
+//   2. retrieval_key = SHA-256(canonical rootless URN).
+//   3. POST JSON-RPC 2.0 `dig.getContent` to the configured DIG RPC endpoint
